{"tid":1970372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【正視聽】CCTVB講嗰個香港最美「逆行者」 - 武漢亞心醫院院長謝俊明其實係支那人","createTime":"2020-04-13T06:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T07:29:03.000Z","uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c88fc525d1bb962895e91d69f3507f791919373b","tid":1970372,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話説老豆睇緊CCTVB新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCCTVB 話有個香港人係武漢開左間醫院，幫係湖北香港人入院治療，幫左香港人好多，講到好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港商謝俊明在亞洲開設五間私家醫療機構，其中兩間在武漢，他在武漢封城前連夜趕回來同前線共同抗疫。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n仲話武漢抗疫過程，唔少做法值得香港參考。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ke0TxCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKe0TxCG.jpg&h=b574b871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiV4EhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBiV4EhP.jpg&h=fdf48cde&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聼左幾秒，覺得條友講廣東話有D鄉音，加埋個樣有D大陸柒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=335huv3/ctp-vzntr/15330306693177n84417s0o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D335huv3%2Fctp-vzntr%2F15330306693177n84417s0o.jpg&h=01c31222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是上網Google左一下，但原來個個院長係假香港人，實情係支那人扮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wSJRjjU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwSJRjjU.jpg&h=8694afb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6dd0b0959ccc409bba2d6490c50d0d8e23eb4b8","tid":1970372,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"港人港人，港佢老味咩腥港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}